          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Derivatives Fairness Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal banking agencies from requiring banking institutions, for the purposes of risk-based capital requirements, to hold capital against certain derivative contracts.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-19T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
